Project Status - March 28, 2026
🚀 Accomplishments (Today)
1. Authentication & Google OAuth
Integration: Successfully integrated django-allauth with Google as a social provider.
UI Styling: Designed premium login and signup pages using a consistent Sage & Terracotta aesthetic.
Security: Fixed historical 405 errors by converting logout to a secure POST method.
Access Control: Secured the donate view to ensure all contributions are linked to a registered user.
2. Dynamic Data Infrastructure
Global Impact: Created the ImpactStatistic model to manage homepage metrics from the Admin.
Real-time Analytics: Updated the Dashboard and Hero sections to pull live data from the database.
Automatic Tracking: Form submissions (Volunteers, Donations) now automatically associate with the logged-in user for impact tracking.
3. UI/UX Refinements
Conditional Header: Implemented logic to dynamically show Dashboard/Sign Out links for logged-in users.
Syncing: Synchronized the "Our Changemakers" and "Campaigns Led" metrics across the public and private sides of the site.
📅 Roadmap (Tomorrow)
1. Advanced Access Control & Profiles
 Staff-Only Dashboard: Restrict management tools to NGO owners only.
 User Contribution Profiles: Create a simple view for regular users to see their donation history.
2. Modular Project Gallery
 Dynamic Gallery: Build a component to showcase different NGO projects (e.g., individual student seeds).
 Project Models: Add models to track specific project milestones and updates.
3. Production Readiness
 Production Email: Transition from console-based emails to a real SMTP provider (e.g., SendGrid).
 Data Validation: Review form logic to ensure robust data entry.
